1
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:42,370
Here.

2
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:43,620
Drink a little.

3
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:46,320
Just drink a little more and you'll be fine.

4
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,520
It's finally over.

5
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,040
I need to be taken care of.

6
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:55,120
I've been taking care of you for half the day.

7
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:55,980
That's enough.

8
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:57,600
I'm weak.

9
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:01,490
I'll get you another bowl of tonic.

10
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,300
I don't want to take medicine.

11
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,690
Then I'll go buy you some supplements.

12
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:11,080
Brother Wuzhou,

13
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:12,240
are you going out too?

14
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:12,520
Yes.

15
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,039
Danyu,

16
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,320
Xiaoxue

17
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:15,520
is a bit weak.

18
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:18,580
I'm going out to buy some fresh spiritual herbs for her.

19
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:19,520
By the way,

20
00:01:19,520 --> 00:01:20,450
where is Shishi?

21
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,800
Shishi?

22
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,840
Hurry up.

23
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,280
Isn't that Danyu?

24
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,160
Isn't it?

25
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:36,900
Then where could Danyu have gone?

26
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:53,680
Brother Wuzhou.

27
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,360
Look.

28
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:59,039
Disciples of Tiandao Palace.

29
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:02,930
They must be going to the village to deal with the aftermath.

30
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:04,680
As expected of Tiandao Palace.

31
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,880
They are really fast.

32
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,760
Brother Wuzhou.

33
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,600
They look so powerful.

34
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,759
So,

35
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:13,040
does Tiandao Palace have a high status?

36
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:13,640
Danyu,

37
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,140
Tiandao Palace

38
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,400
is the leader of the human race.

39
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,400
It has guarded the human race for thousands of years.

40
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,400
Since childhood,

41
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:21,360
we have had so many memories about Tiandao Palace.

42
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,360
Why

43
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:24,200
do you seem to remember nothing?

44
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,700
Could it be that

45
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,360
the injuries you suffered in the village

46
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,760
have left some sequelae?

47
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,360
Could it be that

48
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,900
your brain is damaged?

49
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:33,960
No.

50
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,160
Brother Wuzhou,

51
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,720
I just couldn't remember it for a moment.

52
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,780
It's not a sequela.

53
00:02:38,079 --> 00:02:39,210
I'm perfectly fine.

54
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,240
Really.

55
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,280
I don't believe you.

56
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:41,600
No.

57
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:44,380
I have to find you some more medicine.

58
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,320
I don't want to take my medicine.

59
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:55,520
Here,

60
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,860
your supplements.

61
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,160
I won't take this.

62
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,800
Free ones are better.

63
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:06,960
This is what you get for now.

64
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,040
I'll go check with Sister Mu

65
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,640
if she has anything better.

66
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,680
What should I do?

67
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,680
Is my current role

68
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:19,120
completely reduced to an emergency ration?

69
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,600
Even though he saved me,

70
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:22,180
that's a separate matter.

71
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:25,200
Can he stop looking at me like I'm food?

72
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,600
Yiyi.

73
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,600
I need you so much.

74
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,880
You should've told me before you left

75
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,940
whether this demon king eats people.

76
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:36,840
I don't taste good at all.

77
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,640
Danyu,

78
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,280
I finally found you.

79
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:41,880
What are you muttering about?

80
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:43,280
What's tasty or not?

81
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,320
Shishi,

82
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,160
morning.

83
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,160
I mean

84
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,100
the medicine doesn't taste good.

85
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:48,880
Yeah.

86
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:50,680
I've been taking so much medicine lately

87
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,680
that I've lost my appetite for food.

88
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,200
Right,

89
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:53,720
Danyu.

90
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:56,180
I've been looking for you for a long time.

91
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,520
Why are you at his door?

92
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,280
I just

93
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:03,080
went to buy something for him.

94
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:04,080
What?

95
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,520
You bought him something?

96
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,450
What did you buy?

97
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,370
Did you buy anything for me?

98
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,440
I...

99
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,760
I want something too.

100
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,280
Is it the one on the table?

101
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,040
Shishi.

102
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,250
You haven't touched it.

103
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,160
It seems

104
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,480
you don't want to eat it.

105
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,740
Then I'll help myself.

106
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:26,640
This is mine now.

107
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,280
Shishi,

108
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,000
don't.

109
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,360
Smells so good.

110
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,490
As expected of what you bought, Danyu.

111
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,200
Shishi.

112
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,450
Let's talk outside.

113
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,610
Let's talk outside.

114
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:46,520
Danyu.

115
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:51,480
Move over.

116
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,200
Danyu,

117
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,280
good morning.

118
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,100
Are you waiting to eat with me?

119
00:04:58,840 --> 00:04:59,240
Eat.

120
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,320
Let's all eat.

121
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:02,360
We've all been through hardships together.

122
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,040
We are good brothers.

123
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,140
Come on.

124
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:05,880
Eat, eat, eat.

125
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:06,940
Eat more, eat more.

126
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:10,380
You eat.

127
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:11,280
Eat.

128
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:18,680
Danyu,

129
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,040
are you ready for bed?

130
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,560
Danyu,

131
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,300
let me sleep with you tonight.

132
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:25,160
I'm used to sleeping alone.

133
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,000
I'll pass.

134
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:29,520
But I want you to keep me company.

135
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,640
Just keep me company.

136
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,480
How about this.

137
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,480
Let's play a game.

138
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:36,760
The loser drinks.

139
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,280
Once you're drunk,

140
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:40,280
you won't bother me anymore, right?

141
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:41,920
Danyu,

142
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,560
do you just want to drink with me?

143
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,440
We can just drink without playing.

144
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:45,840
No.

145
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,760
I really just want

146
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:48,640
to play games.

147
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,320
What game is so fun?

148
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:51,640
Count me in.

149
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:53,640
No need.

150
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,840
This is a game for Danyu and me.

151
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,090
Why are you joining?

152
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,200
It's fine, it's fine.

153
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,580
The more, the merrier.

154
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,020
That's roughly the rules.

155
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,120
Whoever guesses the closest number

156
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,880
wins.

157
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,340
Is everyone clear?

158
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:20,640
I'll go first.

159
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,520
Three fives.

160
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:28,420
Four fours.

161
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:30,760
Six threes.

162
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,760
Seven sixes.

163
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,080
Open.

164
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,040
I don't have any sixes.

165
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,040
I actually lost.

166
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,360
Again.

167
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:56,780
Four sixes.

168
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:57,880
Five twos.

169
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:01,960
Six fives.

170
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,290
Seven sixes.

171
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,410
Eight fives.

172
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:06,730
Open.

173
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,960
Why?

174
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,600
Why do I always lose

175
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,200
when I don't have the points?

176
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,000
Again.

177
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,180
Open it.

178
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:29,820
Open it.

179
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:30,540
Open it.

180
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:50,640
Drunk so quickly.

181
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,000
You are useless.

182
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:55,040
This blatant cheating,

183
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:57,520
only Shishi thinks there is no problem.

184
00:07:57,720 --> 00:08:00,360
But she guesses whatever points she doesn't have.

185
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,560
This gambling addiction,

186
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,640
only she has it.

187
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,400
But next,

188
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:06,800
we can play

189
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,320
just the two of us.

190
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,720
With your tricks,

191
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:12,170
I'm afraid I'll die in your hands tonight.

192
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,920
It's a bit too late today.

193
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,560
Let's play happily next time.

194
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,000
It seems she is in the way.

195
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:19,440
It's better to let her disappear.

196
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,120
Exactly.

197
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,400
I'll make her disappear immediately.
